**Story** 
Once upon a time , in a forest , there lived a monkey who resided on a jamun tree.
In the same forest, there lived a crocodlie and his wife 
one day , the crocodile came to the bank of the river yamuna and rested under the tree.
The kind monkey offered his some fruits .The crocodile came back the next day for  more fruits , as he loved them .
As days passed by , the crocodile and the monkey became good friends